{
  "stem": "1413.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He brought me back every penny of it-- 131 mark and 20 pennies for 100 guilder at the time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What am I going to do with money in concentration camp?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I work at the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I work, you name it, Ukrainians, Russian, French, New Zealanders, Australia's, you name it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody works there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Australians, and the English, and the French that were prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And even a name on that list what I got here, and men worked for union labor in the Netherlands.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the soldiers, one of the PO-- POW from England, I think-- or from Australia-- I'm-- I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They got to talk to each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that man, that soldier, saw to it that he got all the bread from the guy's leftover.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he got it because they worked for the same company at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His name, I got him here, [NON-ENGLISH] was his name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wander off a little bit, I know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] I forgot where I was, because I wandered off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, OK, that guy who who put the-- took the cement sack with me, brought me everything back, all the money back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the next time when he went to the Netherlands again-- maybe two, three, four months later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And maybe it was not him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And maybe it was another man that they did some-- that was more than one who was willing to do it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He brought me back food from my sister-in-law.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My sister-in-law gave him food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He got a ginger cake that was so long that he had to give it in half.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And how could he hand it to me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no way he could hand it to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
